--- View ---

Super + Alt + Up            # Maximize panel
Ctrl + W                    # Close Editor


--- Navigating ---

Ctrl + P                    # Open any file by name
Ctrl + Alt + -              # Navigate backwards in editor
Ctrl + Shift + -            # Navigate forwards in editor
F12                         # Go to the definition

--- Editing ---

Alt + Shift + [Up/Down]     # Multiline select up or down
Alt + Shift + LClick        # Multiline select on cursor
Ctrl + Shift + L            # Multiline select on current selected word
